category: X11
requires: cygwin libglib2.0_0 libgtk2.0_0 libintl8 libpango1.0_0 libvte9 libX11_6 lua
sdesc: "Simple terminal emulator based on vte library, extensible via Lua"
ldesc: "TermIt is a simple terminal emulator based on vte library with a lot
of features:
 * tabs
 * bookmarks
 * sessions
 * changing tab name
 * changing font for tabs
 * encodings (all available from GTK2)
 * integrated lua interpreter
Configuration can be changed via $HOME/.config/termit/termit.cfg file."
